_mTdug"><h2 class="screen-reader-text">Disclosure</h2><p class="reviewDisclosure_disclosure___xnWQ"><a href="/">NCOA</a> <!-- -->is supported in part by commissions earned from purchases made through shared affiliate links.<!-- --> <a href="/product-resources/page/how-we-research-test-and-review-products-and-services/">Learn more.</a></p></div><article class="styles_container__ezDSU"><header class="reviewHeader_container__wDAp3"><div class="reviewHeader_details__WCxIE"><div class="reviewHeader_headlineStack__yNXoo"><h1 class="heading_heading__8mSev heading_h1__1NQVK heading_heading-size-m__cipmF">The Best Medical Alert Systems of 2025: Tested and Reviewed</h1><p class="reviewHeader_subHeading__bZKZp">We put the best medical alert system brands to the test—see which 6 rose above the rest to make our list.</p><div class="reviewHeader_articleMeta__P6kI_"><div class="articleMeta_articleMeta__DF5hB"><time dateTime="2025-12-22T05:00:00Z">Dec 22, 2025</time><div><button class="printButton_printButton__Mx3tQ" type="button"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 19 17" aria-hidden="true" tab-index="-1"><path d="M4.224 16.75v-2.44c0-1.86 1.52-3.355 3.414-3.355h7.138v5.795zm-2.203-3.66h.651v-2.44c0-.518.435-.915.931-.915h11.794c.527 0 .93.427.93.915v2.44h.652c.838 0 1.521-.67 1.521-1.494v-5.49c0-1.19-.993-2.196-2.235-2.196H2.736C1.524 3.91.5 4.886.5 6.106v5.49c0 .793.683 1.494 1.52 1.494Zm2.204-10.4c0-1.342 1.117-2.44 2.482-2.44h8.07v2.44z"></path></svg><span>Print Page</span></button></div><div><button type="button" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="false" id="react-aria-:RhldjtssvfaH1:" class="socialShare_shareButton__wR6m6" data-rac=""><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" tab-index="-1"><path fill="#00645F" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M13.782.357c-.47 0-.935.102-1.362.298a3.2 3.2 0 0 0-1.106.84 3.133 3.133 0 0 0-.7 2.598L5.934 7.327a1 1 0 0 0-.068.051 3.255 3.255 0 0 0-3.391-.352c-.542.26-.999.667-1.318 1.171a3.14 