  <li>We chose <a data-item-id="bbafe99b-3100-4a6c-b177-ae83d36d0f52" href="https://www.medicalguardian.com/ncoa?aid=4735&amp;utm_source=NCOA&amp;utm_Medium=Referral&amp;utm_campaign=bestmedicalalertsystems-ncoa" target="_blank" rel="sponsored nofollow">Medical Guardian</a> as the best medical alert system of 2025 for its fast response time, unique features, and competitive pricing.</li>
