<h2 id="our-reviews-of-the-top-medical-alert-systems">Our reviews of the top medical alert systems</h2>
<h2 id="medical-guardian-best-overall">Medical Guardian: Best Overall</h2>
<p>We chose Medical Guardian as our Best Overall medical alert system because it has one of the fastest average response times, a long battery life, and a great mix of helpful features and a variety of device types and styles. When we evaluated features and tested the devices ourselves, we gave Medical Guardian a score of 9.9/10.</p>
