  </li>
</ul></div></div></div></div><!--/$-->
<h2 id="medical-alert-easiest-setup">Medical Alert: Easiest Setup</h2>
<p>We chose Medical Alert as the Easiest Setup because our testers found <a href="/product-resources/medical-alert-systems/medical-alert-review/">Medical Alert</a> very easy to use straight out of the box. All directions were laid out clearly with visual cues. Medical Alert got a perfect 5/5 score for unboxing and ease of setup. </p>
