<h2 id="lifestation-best-for-caregivers">LifeStation: Best for Caregivers</h2>
<p>We named LifeStation as our Best for Caregivers for its easy location tracking. If a care partner is worried about someone with a LifeStation device, they can simply text LifeStation and receive a location update. If a phone isn’t handy, you can ask an Amazon Alexa paired with the LifeStation device. These features can offer peace of mind for LifeStation users and those who care for them, ensuring you can always check in. </p>
<section class="component-review-product reviewProduct_container__Lnd_S"><header class="reviewProduct_header__RVIfE reviewProduct_hasPrimaryImage__T5ENZ"><div class="reviewProduct_headerText__3pI1F"><h3 class="reviewProduct_heading__hRSem heading_heading__8mSev heading_h3__nTE01 heading_heading-size-s__UqyXs">LifeStation</h3><span class="topicLink_container__vB6zg reviewProduct_eyebrow__rr2VV">Best for Caregivers</span><aside class="reviewProduct_accreditation__HVah5"><div class="ratingDisplay_ratingContainer___9j6N"><span><span class="ratingDisplay_rating__bRHFT">8.9</span><span class="ratingDisplay_srText__LGLkF"> out of </span><span class="ratingDisplay_ratingMax__EJxmn">10</span></span><span class="ratingDisplay_ratingText__hZ27n">Very Good</span></div></aside><div class="reviewProduct_ctasContainer__bwLGG desktop-only"><div class="reviewProduct_headerCtas__HAing"><div class="reviewProduct_phoneCta__3rROC"><span class="reviewProduct_phoneIcon__rxYWv"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 26 27"><path stroke="#0B4A5D" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.219" d="M16.696 15.261a.81.81 0 0 1 .77-.07l4.79 2.146a.81.81 0 0 1 .488.843 4.91 4.91 0 0 1-4.869 4.258A13.813 13.813 0 0 1 4.062 8.625 4.91 4.91 0 0 1 8.32 3.756a.81.81 0 0 1 .843.488l2.146 4.793a.81.81 0 0 1-.067.765l-2.17 2.58a.8.8 0 0 0-.055.794c.84 1.72 2.617 3.476 4.341 4.307a.8.8 0 0 0 .796-.06z"></path></svg></span><a class="reviewProduct_phoneLink___93Td" href="tel:8778210447">(877) 821-0447</a></div><a class="button-cta reviewProduct_buttonCta__KxiJp buttonCta_buttonSizeMedium__QtIRK buttonCta_buttonThemeGreen__gOx_M buttonCta_isFullWidthOnMobile__gbLo0" href="https://buy.lifestation.com/ncoa-o/?conid=110&amp;utm_source=ncoa_organic&amp;utm_id=bestmedicalalertsystems-ncoa" target="_blank" rel="sponsored nofollow">Visit Site</a></div></div></div><div class="reviewProduct_headerImage__eRb4s"><figure class="imageWrapper_imageWrapper__eiLsy primary-image