<div class="reviewAccordion_accordion__EHnyL"><div class="toggle_container__ZNCKu"><div class="toggle_toggleButton__Ix9nG"><button aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="toggle-content-pros-and-cons" id="toggle-button-pros-and-cons" type="button" class="toggle-button"><span class="reviewAccordion_accordionButton__7yyCP">Pros and cons</span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="toggle-button-pros-and-cons" class="toggle-content" id="toggle-content-pros-and-cons" role="region"><div class="reviewAccordion_accordionContent__nlTmM"><div class="render-html renderHTML_renderHTML__bHC6S"><div class="prosConsList_container__ghGvf component-pros-cons-list"><div class="prosConsList_prosContainer__NuM9J"><h4 class="prosConsList_heading__5TEhA">Pros</h4><ul class="prosConsList_list__OrpnP"><li><div class="render-html renderHTML_renderHTML__bHC6S">Pairs with Amazon Alexa</div></li><li><div class="render-html renderHTML_renderHTML__bHC6S">GPS-enabled location tracking on mobile devices</div></li><li><div class="render-html renderHTML_renderHTML__bHC6S">Easy to set up and use</div></li><li><div class="render-html renderHTML_renderHTML__bHC6S">Long battery life</div></li></ul></div><div class="prosConsList_consContainer__pp9UO"><h4 class="prosConsList_heading__5TEhA">Cons</h4><ul class="prosConsList_list__OrpnP"><li><div class="render-html renderHTML_renderHTML__bHC6S">No mobile app</div></li><li><div class="render-html renderHTML_renderHTML__bHC6S">One of the most expensive options</div></li><li><div class="render-html renderHTML_renderHTML__bHC6S">Unclear plans listed on website</div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section>
<!--$--><div class="readMoreSection_readMoreSection__AGiM_"><div class="readMoreSection_contentWrapper__RfJnz"><div data-type="review" class="bodyContentReview_bodyContent__WxmOI bodyContentReview_bodyContent__WxmOI"><div class="render-html renderHTMLReview_renderHTML__ykeTL"><h3>Our experience with LifeStation</h3>
<p><strong>What we like: </strong>Our testers found LifeStation easy to set up and start using. The instructions were easy to follow, and all of the devices, which include one home device and three on-the-go options, were ready to use immediately. But what really stood out to our team was LifeStation’s easy location-tracking options. If a care partner wants to check in on a LifeStation user’s location, they just need to send a text to receive a real-time location update. While the brand doesn’t offer its own app, it integrates with Amazon Alexa devices, so once paired, care partners can use Alexa devices or the Alexa app for updates. </p>
<p>LifeStation’s Sidekick Home uses a cellular connection to keep users covered within 1,300 feet of the base station. The brand’s mobile devices include the Sidekick and the Pearl, both designed to be worn as necklaces, as well as the Sidekick Smart Watch. </p>
<p><em>Other things we like: </em></p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Accurate location tracking: </strong>LifeStation has its own unique algorithm for location tracking, which uses GPS and WiFi for more accurate results.</li>
  <li><strong>No contracts:</strong> LifeStation does not require a contract for any of its devices. Users can cancel their service with the medical alert company at any time.</li>
  <li><strong>One monitoring fee:</strong> Households where more than one member could benefit from a medical alert system only need to pay one monitoring fee. An extra help button costs only $3.99 a month.</li>
  <li><strong>Fast response time</strong>: LifeStation had the second-fastest response time among the medical alert systems we tested. Only LifeFone was faster.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>What could be better: </strong>We found cost to be the biggest drawback of LifeStation. While the Sidekick Home’s starting monthly fee is the same as Medical Guardian’s ($36.99/month), you’ll also need to pay $12.50 in shipping. Users will also need to purchase LifeStation’s protection plan for an extra $8/month in order to add fall detection, which costs another $8/month. So the final cost of the At Home plan with fall detection is $52.95/month. Since you’re not required to add the protection plan to Medical Guardian in order to get fall detection, its cost is $48.95/month. </p>
<p><em>Other things we wish were better:</em></p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>No LifeStation app: </strong>While LifeStation does make it easy for care partners to check in through text and Amazon’s Alexa, it doesn’t have its own designated app. While there is a solid workaround, some users may find this a drawback.</li>
  <li><strong>No home landline system: </strong>LifeStation only offers its Sidekick Home with a cellular connection. Those who have limited cellular coverage don’t have a landline option.</li>
  <li><strong>Unclear plans: </strong>LifeStation breaks out its plans into Standard, Select, and Supreme. Yet there’s no mention of the different options until you’ve already clicked “buy now.”  </li>
</ul>
<h3>LifeStation&#x27;s performance in our tests</h3>
<p>Our testers were impressed by how easily they were able to set up the LifeStation devices. They had no problems getting the brand’s products up and running. “Set up was as easy as unboxing and putting the watch on the wrist. There was nothing else required to get the device up and running,” one tester said of the Sidekick Smart Watch. A different tester said setting up the Sidekick was “easy peasy!”</p>
<figure class="imageWrapper_imageWrapper__eiLsy image-wrapper"><img alt="The LifeStation Sidekick Home base station and three wearable buttons" type="image/jpeg" loading="lazy" width="800" height="600" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="image-wrapper-image" style="color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1200px) 50vw, 696px" srcSet="/_next/image/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview-assets-us-01.kc-usercontent.com%3A443%2Fffacfe7d-10b6-0083-2632-604077fd4eca%2F897f5674-9165-442a-8cad-1b39c770b181%2FLifeStationSidekickHome.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview-assets-us-01.kc-usercontent.com%3A443%2Fffacfe7d-10b6-0083-2632-604077fd4eca%2F897f5674-9165-442a-8cad-1b39c770b181%2FLifeStationSidekickHome.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview-assets-us-01.kc-usercontent.com%3A443%2Fffacfe7d-10b6-0083-2632-604077fd4eca%2F897f5674-9165-442a-8cad-1b39c770b181%2FLifeStationSidekickHome.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview-assets-us-01.kc-usercontent.com%3A443%2Fffacfe7d-10b6-0083-2632-604077fd4eca%2F897f5674-9165-442a-8cad-1b39c770b181%2FLifeStationSidekickHome.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview-assets-us-01.kc-usercontent.com%3A443%2Fffacfe7d-10b6-0083-2632-604077fd4eca%2F897f5674-9165-442a-8cad-1b39c770b181%2FLifeStationSidekickHome.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview-assets-us-01.kc-usercontent.com%3A443%2Fffacfe7d-10b6-0083-2632-604077fd4eca%2F897f5674-9165-442a-8cad-1b39c770b181%2FLifeStationSidekickHome.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview-assets-us-01.kc-usercontent.com%3A443%2Fffacfe7d-10b6-0083-2632-604077fd4eca%2F897f5674-9165-442a-8cad-1b39c770b181%2FLifeStationSidekickHome.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview-assets-us-01.kc-usercontent.com%3A443%2Fffacfe7d-10b6-0083-2632-604077fd4eca%2F897f5674-9165-442a-8cad-1b39c770b181%2FLifeStationSidekickHome.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview-assets-us-01.kc-usercontent.com%3A443%2Fffacfe7d-10b6-0083-2632-604077fd4eca%2F897f5674-9165-442a-8cad-1b39c770b181%2FLifeStationSidekickHome.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/_next/image/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview-assets-us-01.kc-usercontent.com%3A443%2Fffacfe7d-10b6-0083-2632-604077fd4eca%2F897f5674-9165-442a-8cad-1b39c770b181%2FLifeStationSidekickHome.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/><figcaption>The LifeStation Sidekick Home comes with a base station and wearable buttons, so users can access help throughout their homes.</figcaption></figure>
<p>We loved that the Sidekick has a separate testing button. Our testers have tried a lot of medical alert systems, and any feature that encourages testing the devices is a definite benefit. We’ve heard from a lot of medical alert users who are reluctant to “bother anyone” with a false alarm or test. The Sidekick’s separate testing button quiets those concerns. “They recommend you test your device once a month, so they made it very easy to do,” one of our testers said. </p>
<p>Another LifeStation feature our testers like is the ability to cancel a call. All of the brand’s on-the-go devices allow for call cancellations. This is another feature that can ease concerns around accidentally pressing the device&#x27;s buttons. </p>
<p>Our testers also raved about LifeStation’s mobile devices for their simple design and ease of use. “I really love how intuitive and simple this device is,&quot; one of our testers said about the LifeStation Pearl. &quot;I tested it and exclaimed, &#x27;How does this little device work like a cell phone?&#x27; I think if you are worried about getting assistance for falling or having a medical emergency, this is a no-brainer. It&#x27;s easy to use, affordable, and great for peace of mind.”</p>
<h3>Comparing LifeStation models</h3>
<div class="render-html-table-wrapper"><table class="render-html-table"><tbody><tr><td><br/></td><td><strong>Sidekick Home</strong></td><td><strong>Sidekick</strong></td><td><strong>Sidekick Smart </strong></td><td><strong>Pearl</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Starting monthly cost</strong></td><td>$36.95</td><td>$40.95</td><td>$48.95</td><td>$50.95</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Programming fee</strong></td><td>None</td><td>$99.95</td><td>$99.95</td><td>$99.95</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Device type</strong></td><td>At-home</td><td>GPS</td><td>GPS</td><td>GPS</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Max. battery life</strong></td><td>N/A</td><td>5 days</td><td>1 day</td><td>3 days</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Standout feature</strong></td><td>At-home cellular system</td><td>Mobile device with the longest battery life</td><td>Discreet, Smart Watch design</td><td>Lightest and smallest option</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<h4>The LifeStation customer experience</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Warranty: </strong>No warranty</li>
  <li><strong>Trial period: </strong>30-day risk-free trial for all devices.</li>
  <li><strong>Customer service: </strong>If you need additional assistance, you can visit the <a href="https://www.lifestation.com/contact-lifestation/" data-new-window="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LifeStation customer service page</a>.</li>
  <li><strong>Phone</strong>: <a href="tel:800-998-2400">800-998-2400</a>, Monday through Friday, during normal working hours</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div><!--/$-->
<h2 id="lifefone-longest-battery-life">LifeFone: Longest Battery Life</h2>
<p>LifeFone earned our ranking as the Longest Battery Life because it has far and away the longest lifespan of any device we’ve tested. At 10 full days for the At-Home and On-the-Go VIPx, LifeFone’s devices have double the next-longest battery life on the list. It’s a feature that contributed to LifeFone’s 9.4/10 score in our testing.</p>
<section class="component-review-product reviewProduct_container__Lnd_S"><header class="reviewProduct_header__RVIfE reviewProduct_hasPrimaryImage__T5ENZ"><div class="reviewProduct_headerText__3pI1F"><h3 class="reviewProduct_heading__hRSem heading_heading__8mSev heading_h3__nTE01 heading_heading-size-s__UqyXs">LifeFone</h3><span class="topicLink_container__vB6zg reviewProduct_eyebrow__rr2VV">Longest Battery Life</span><aside class="reviewProduct_accreditation__HVah5"><div class="ratingDisplay_ratingContainer___9j6N"><span><span class="ratingDisplay_rating__bRHFT">9.4</span><span class="ratingDisplay_srText__LGLkF"> out of </span><span class="ratingDisplay_ratingMax__EJxmn">10</span></span><span class="ratingDisplay_ratingText__hZ27n">Excellent</span></div></aside><div class="reviewProduct_ctasContainer__bwLGG desktop-only"><div class="reviewProduct_headerCtas__HAing"><div class="reviewProduct_phoneCta__3rROC"><span class="reviewProduct_phoneIcon__rxYWv"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 26 27"><path stroke="#0B4A5D" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.219" d="M16.696 15.261a.81.81 0 0 1 .77-.07l4.79 2.146a.81.81 0 0 1 .488.843 4.91 4.91 0 0 1-4.869 4.258A13.813 13.813 0 0 1 4.062 8.625 4.91 4.91 0 0 1 8.32 3.756a.81.81 0 0 1 .843.488l2.146 4.793a.81.81 0 0 1-.067.765l-2.17 2.58a.8.8 0 0 0-.055.794c.84 1.72 2.617 3.476 4.341 4.307a.8.8 0 0 0 .796-.06z"></path></svg></span><a class="reviewProduct_phoneLink___93Td" href="tel:8662211936">(866) 221-1936</a></div><a class="button-cta reviewProduct_buttonCta__KxiJp buttonCta_buttonSizeMedium__QtIRK buttonCta_buttonThemeGreen__gOx_M buttonCta_isFullWidthOnMobile__gbLo0" href="https://www.lifefone.com/partners-landing?st-t=NCOA&amp;utm_source=NCOA&amp;subID=bestmedicalalertsystems-ncoa" target="_blank" rel="sponsored nofollow">Visit Site</a></div></div></div><div class="reviewProduct_headerImage__eRb4s"><figure class="imageWrapper_imageWrapper__eiLsy primary-image imag